xlsform_compare 


check <- xlsform_compare(listfile = c( "demo.xlsx","demo_adapt1.xlsx","demo_adapt2.xlsx"),  
                         folder = stringr::str_sub(system.file("", package = "XlsFormPrettyPrint"), end = -1) ,                    
                         label_language = NULL,
                         fileout = NULL)
